history.content:
As the name implies, no one is ADDED to a class after the add/drop deadline. Not even from the wait list. If waitlist continued to process after the add/drop deadline there would be no point to having a deadline.

To avoid confusion, I will purge all CompSci wait lists after the add/drop deadline passes so people are clear that they no longer have a chance of being enrolled.

Hi all! I have the following question. Suppose I am on the waitlist for a class. Then, after the add/drop deadline, will I be dropped from the waitlist by the system? Or will I remain on the waitlist but I can not drop by myself anymore?
history.subject: Waitlist after add/drop deadline?
